headline: Marsh McLennan Agency Acquires Olympic Insurance Agency
summary: WHITE PLAINS, N.Y., August 01, 2025--Marsh McLennan Agency (MMA), a business of Marsh and a leading provider of business insurance, employee health and benefits, retirement and wealth, and private client insurance solutions across the US and Canada, today announced the acquisition of Olympic Insurance Agency, a Simi Valley, California-based independent insurance agency. Terms of the acquisition were not disclosed.
